00:00:00,040 --> 00:00:14,740
( Watch on Kissasia.vip )

1
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:02,900
=Daughter of Fortune=

2
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,460
(Adapted from the novel
"Phoenix Palace Dream" by Lan Jiujiu)

3
00:01:05,540 --> 00:01:08,460
=Episode 11=

4
00:01:09,020 --> 00:01:10,390
They composed a full hundred poems.

5
00:01:13,380 --> 00:01:14,680
What has Your Majesty discovered?

6
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:15,719
Hmm.

7
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:22,959
Interesting.

8
00:01:23,799 --> 00:01:25,519
One person wrote only of love,

9
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:27,959
while the other wrote only
of lofty ambition.

10
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:30,719
Women are easily consumed by love.

11
00:01:30,719 --> 00:01:32,690
Naturally, their poems
are filled with tenderness.

12
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,959
Men are different.

13
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,830
Their hearts are always
set on greater ambitions.

14
00:01:35,840 --> 00:01:36,959
The poems about ambition

15
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,599
were written by Shen Zhinian.

16
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:41,760
These love poems
were written by Lu Jianglin.

17
00:01:42,719 --> 00:01:44,760
So Lu Jianglin
is quite the hopeless romantic.

18
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,560
If he truly were devoted,

19
00:01:46,780 --> 00:01:48,079
he would've stopped Shen Zhinian

20
00:01:48,079 --> 00:01:49,450
before she ever entered the palace.

21
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:50,519
That's true.

22
00:01:50,900 --> 00:01:52,159
If he really were so lovestruck,

23
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:53,690
he wouldn't have married Shen Nanqiao.

24
00:01:55,280 --> 00:01:57,319
Lu Jianglin is no threat.

25
00:01:58,439 --> 00:01:59,760
But this Jiang Chen...

26
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,959
Why has he suddenly
become so attentive to Shen Zhinian?

27
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,040
Keep an eye on him.

28
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,280
Understood.

29
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:09,950
Your Majesty should visit Physician Lu
to change your medicine.

30
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:12,460
Physician Lu specifically warned
that it must not be delayed.

31
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:13,439
Mm.

32
00:02:13,879 --> 00:02:14,759
Let's go.

33
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:18,120
Luckily, I got the medicine last night.

34
00:02:18,600 --> 00:02:20,360
Today, Wen Ling went
to the Imperial Hospital

35
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:22,120
and took away every ointment for itching.

36
00:02:22,639 --> 00:02:24,800
Young Master, you explained
that the rash came

37
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:26,000
from insect bites today.

38
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:27,790
I wonder
whether His Majesty believed him.

39
00:02:28,080 --> 00:02:29,199
He's far too suspicious.

40
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:30,919
He won't believe it that easily.

41
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:32,599
Then what should we do?

42
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,159
He is the ruler,

43
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,439
and I am his subject.

44
00:02:35,700 --> 00:02:37,780
If he refuses to trust me,
there's nothing I can do.

45
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:39,759
That Shen Zhinian really is capable.

46
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:42,390
She actually managed
to draw His Majesty to the Cold Palace.

47
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:44,660
Not only did he go to the Cold Palace,

48
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,800
he even tried climbing in
through the window.

49
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:49,639
Shen Zhinian truly is special to him.

50
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:53,990
Spread the news that His Majesty visited
the Cold Palace last night.

51
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:55,800
Lady Liu,

52
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,400
Liu Ruyan,

53
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:57,080
Shen Nanqiao...

54
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:58,210
Don't leave a single one out.

55
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,790
Young Master, you have always
stayed out of harem affairs

56
00:03:01,479 --> 00:03:03,240
and have gotten along well
with His Majesty.

57
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:06,879
Why are you suddenly
so concerned about Shen Zhinian?

58
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,639
Because His Majesty cares about her.

59
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,479
Lady Liu,

60
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:31,360
Nanqiao is one of our Liu family.

61
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:34,039
You should look after her
more in the future.

62
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:37,210
Dowager Consort, be careful
not to bring trouble upon yourself.

63
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,960
I know exactly what I'm doing.

64
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:48,500
(May everlasting kindness
and glory remain)

65
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:50,199
Young Master Lu,

66
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,039
you truly write remarkable poetry.

67
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,800
Lu began studying at the age of four.

68
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:57,319
By fourteen, his poems were already
renowned throughout Chizhou.

69
00:03:57,879 --> 00:03:59,039
If he's such a gifted poet,

70
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,800
why is he still relying on Shen family?

71
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:05,759
Young Master Lu simply hasn't
had the right opportunity.

72
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,159
With his talent,

73
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:09,280
his day will come sooner or later.

74
00:04:09,719 --> 00:04:10,840
What is he, a firework?

75
00:04:11,039 --> 00:04:12,240
"Soaring into the sky"?

76
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:14,680
Nanqiao and Jianglin

77
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,680
saved my life.

78
00:04:17,439 --> 00:04:19,040
You shouldn't speak so harshly.

79
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:21,319
Good children.

80
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,000
You've kept me company all day.

81
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:24,759
Go back and get some rest.

82
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,759
Now that the Emperor
is promoting reforms

83
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,910
and supporting scholars
from humble backgrounds,

84
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:39,680
Lu Jianglin already enjoys
quite a reputation in Chizhou.

85
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,879
If we can win him over

86
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,600
for the Liu family,

87
00:04:44,519 --> 00:04:46,720
then talented scholars
of humble birth across the realm

88
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,240
will surely flock to us.

89
00:04:49,290 --> 00:04:51,959
If those scholars choose to serve anyone,
they'll serve His Majesty.

90
00:04:52,260 --> 00:04:53,920
The Liu family
are His Majesty's subjects.

91
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,590
How can you think of competing with him?

92
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,160
I can't be bothered arguing with you.

93
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,399
Go back.

94
00:05:08,560 --> 00:05:09,800
Among the women of the Liu clan,

95
00:05:09,959 --> 00:05:12,399
she is by far the most beautiful.

96
00:05:13,759 --> 00:05:16,079
But she's impossible to control.

97
00:05:17,319 --> 00:05:18,160
Dowager Consort,

98
00:05:18,279 --> 00:05:19,639
you still have me.

99
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:22,720
I will do everything I can
to win His Majesty's favor.

100
00:05:22,920 --> 00:05:23,720
You?

101
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:24,399
Mm.

102
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:27,000
You'll already be doing well
if you stop causing trouble.

103
00:05:27,500 --> 00:05:29,279
You were only
just released from confinement.

104
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,680
Behave yourself.

105
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:46,959
(On the day of Beginning
of Spring in my previous life,)

106
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:49,360
(the Shen family was executed in full,)

107
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:51,639
(and my maternal family
was dragged down with them.)

108
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,839
(Now I only have one month left.)

109
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:56,879
(I must obtain the death-exemption medal
as soon as possible.)

110
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:08,240
Young Lady,

111
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,439
do you think His Majesty
will release us soon?

112
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:12,639
Look at tonight's meal. It's so lavish.

113
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:33,480
We still need to stay careful.

114
00:06:33,839 --> 00:06:35,279
You nearly scared me to death.

115
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,399
Here.

116
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:45,990
Young Lady, you haven't had a proper meal
since entering the Cold Palace.

117
00:06:46,160 --> 00:06:48,120
These two drumsticks are both for you.

118
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,759
There are two.

119
00:06:52,199 --> 00:06:53,160
We'll each have one.

120
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:53,920
Eat.

121
00:06:54,879 --> 00:06:55,439
Mm.

122
00:06:59,439 --> 00:07:00,600
Mm, it's delicious.

123
00:07:00,610 --> 00:07:01,690
Young Lady, you should eat too.

124
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,900
The soup is delicious as well.

125
00:07:13,319 --> 00:07:13,959
Handan.

126
00:07:14,079 --> 00:07:15,160
Handan, what's wrong?

127
00:07:15,399 --> 00:07:15,959
Handan!

128
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:18,990
I'll go fetch an imperial physician.

129
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,639
Hold on.

130
00:07:19,839 --> 00:07:20,519
Wait for me.

131
00:07:21,759 --> 00:07:22,600
How dare you!

132
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:23,990
Once you've entered the Cold Palace,

133
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,780
without an imperial decree, you are forbidden
from stepping beyond its main gate.

134
00:07:27,199 --> 00:07:27,759
Move aside.

135
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,000
Shen Zhinian,

136
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,319
you really think

137
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:31,920
His Majesty holds you dear?

138
00:07:32,240 --> 00:07:33,639
If His Majesty truly favored you,

139
00:07:33,639 --> 00:07:35,300
he wouldn't have sent you
to the Cold Palace.

140
00:07:36,199 --> 00:07:36,959
You vile woman!

141
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,759
What are you doing?

142
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:38,839
Let go!

143
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,360
You madwoman!

144
00:07:41,370 --> 00:07:43,500
Even in the Cold Palace,
you're still this arrogant?

145
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,759
Let me tell you something.

146
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:47,879
The people sent into the Cold Palace
only leave on stretchers.

147
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:24,680
Your Highness,

148
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,000
please rest for a while.

149
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,799
Your Highness dreamed
of immortals again last night?

150
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,240
Mm.

151
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:50,279
I dreamed that my immortal

152
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:52,679
would descend on seven colored clouds
to save me

153
00:08:53,919 --> 00:08:54,840
and take me home.

154
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,559
The palace is Your Highness's home.

155
00:08:57,879 --> 00:08:59,919
Please don't say such things outside.

156
00:09:01,399 --> 00:09:02,360
True.

157
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:04,200
Since I'm already here,

158
00:09:05,450 --> 00:09:07,000
I have no choice but to keep living on.

159
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,320
Go on. What does
His Majesty want this time?

160
00:09:12,090 --> 00:09:15,000
Wen Ling said His Majesty has urgent
business and must leave the palace.

161
00:09:15,010 --> 00:09:16,990
He asked Your Ladyship
to watch over the Cold Palace

162
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:18,370
and make sure nothing goes wrong.

163
00:09:18,380 --> 00:09:19,540
As if he's the only busy one.

164
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:20,519
Always occupied.

165
00:09:21,090 --> 00:09:22,960
Not only do I have to
work endlessly for him,

166
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,390
I even have to look after his woman.

167
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,399
Forget it.

168
00:09:25,450 --> 00:09:27,320
If it weren't for leaving
this miserable place,

169
00:09:28,020 --> 00:09:29,590
who would bother making a deal with him?

170
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:30,320
Let's go.

171
00:09:30,330 --> 00:09:31,790
We'll take a look at the Cold Palace.

172
00:09:32,559 --> 00:09:34,440
Zhinian, where are you going?

173
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,440
Move aside.

174
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,840
Didn't you ask me to come see you?

175
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:37,559
Let go of me.

176
00:09:37,560 --> 00:09:39,800
Nian'er, I know how much
you've suffered since childhood.

177
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:40,519
Move aside.

178
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,360
You want to rise to a higher position.

179
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:41,759
Let go of me.

180
00:09:41,759 --> 00:09:42,360
I'm willing to help you.

181
00:09:42,370 --> 00:09:43,990
I only ask that you
look at me once more.

182
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,480
Move aside.

183
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,120
I'm warning you.

184
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,440
Well now.

185
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,720
One devoted lover,

186
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:50,080
one ambitious schemer.

187
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:52,759
Even I find the two
of you quite well matched.

188
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,039
Your Ladyship, Handan has been poisoned.

189
00:09:55,050 --> 00:09:56,370
I was on my way
to fetch an imperial physician.

190
00:09:56,399 --> 00:09:57,330
Do you know what happens

191
00:09:57,340 --> 00:09:59,070
to discarded concubines who leave
the Cold Palace without permission?

192
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,759
Take Shen Zhinian to the imperial prison.

193
00:10:00,760 --> 00:10:01,880
Lock her up for a few days.

194
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,919
Lady Liu, you can't arrest her!

195
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,559
I serve Dowager Consort Liu.

196
00:10:08,210 --> 00:10:09,970
Don't use the Dowager Consort
to pressure me.

197
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:11,519
I answer only to His Majesty.

198
00:10:11,520 --> 00:10:13,470
Take Lu Jianglin
to the imperial prison as well.

199
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:13,960
You...

200
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:17,159
Your Ladyship,
you claim to be the fairest of all.

201
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:18,279
Please,

202
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,720
go to the Cold Palace and check on Handan.

203
00:10:21,519 --> 00:10:22,759
Please save her.

204
00:10:26,639 --> 00:10:28,879
Someone, go inspect the Cold Palace.

205
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,840
If anyone is truly stirring up trouble,

206
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:33,240
I'll personally make them pay for it.

207
00:10:33,879 --> 00:10:34,639
Yes.

208
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:35,879
Nian'er,

209
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,159
listen to me.

210
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:39,039
I serve Dowager Consort Liu.

211
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:41,159
I can definitely
find a way to get you out.

212
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:42,039
Don't panic.

213
00:10:42,190 --> 00:10:42,879
Behave yourself.

214
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:44,639
If you hadn't stopped me,

215
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:47,080
how would Lady Liu have caught me?

216
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:50,000
If anything happens to Handan today,

217
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:51,919
I will never forgive you.

218
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,000
Nian'er,

219
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:54,919
I was framed too.

220
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:56,320
Someone came to report

221
00:10:56,350 --> 00:10:58,279
that you had urgent matters
to discuss with me.

222
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,720
That's why I came to see you.

223
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,720
I was only worried about you.

224
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:04,159
Why are you always so cold toward me?

225
00:11:05,519 --> 00:11:06,879
If I held an official post,

226
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,840
you wouldn't treat me this way.

227
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:11,280
Shouldn't you take
a good look at yourself first?

228
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:12,879
Your character is disgraceful.

229
00:11:12,880 --> 00:11:14,000
You're heartless and disloyal.

230
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:16,639
If you truly held office,
would you still even notice me?

231
00:11:17,480 --> 00:11:19,759
Since when did your words
become so harsh and cutting?

232
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,440
Is that how a proper lady should speak?

233
00:11:21,759 --> 00:11:22,559
And a true gentleman

234
00:11:22,799 --> 00:11:25,600
wouldn't continue courting another woman
after getting married.

235
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,360
I...

236
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:27,080
Lu!

237
00:11:28,399 --> 00:11:29,000
Lu!

238
00:11:29,159 --> 00:11:30,000
Are you alright?

239
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,279
Why are you here?

240
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:33,120
The Dowager Consort ordered your release.

241
00:11:36,519 --> 00:11:37,240
Someone!

242
00:11:37,519 --> 00:11:38,790
By order of Dowager Consort Liu,

243
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:41,120
Shen Zhinian is to receive
the tattoo punishment.

244
00:11:41,279 --> 00:11:41,919
Yes.

245
00:11:42,399 --> 00:11:43,600
Nanqiao, don't!

246
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:44,900
Don't touch her!

247
00:11:45,190 --> 00:11:45,720
Let go of me!

248
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:46,480
Don't touch her!

249
00:11:46,639 --> 00:11:47,600
None of you touch her!

250
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:53,919
Duke Zhen,

251
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,000
we've waited all day

252
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:57,970
and His Majesty still
hasn't ordered her release.

253
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,039
Could it be
that you guessed wrong?

254
00:12:00,040 --> 00:12:02,090
Perhaps His Majesty
never truly intended to favor her.

255
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:05,080
As expected, I was right all along.

256
00:12:05,679 --> 00:12:06,440
His Majesty

257
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,039
must not be in the palace.

258
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,080
Not in the palace?

259
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:13,679
His Majesty has been searching
for the military tally lately.

260
00:12:14,559 --> 00:12:17,000
He doesn't even have time
for the woman he favors.

261
00:12:17,360 --> 00:12:20,360
That means he's already found clues
to the tally's whereabouts.

262
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:23,100
Send people to intercept him immediately.

263
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,159
No matter what,

264
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,840
the military tally must be recovered

265
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,990
before he returns to the palace.

266
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:27,879
Yes.

267
00:12:30,559 --> 00:12:31,159
Hyah!

268
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:33,720
Hyah!

269
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,080
Hyah!

270
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:13,840
♪Broken dreams,
listening to the light rain♪

271
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:20,800
♪Bitter cold, bringing mist to the eyes♪

272
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:24,800
♪If we don't meet♪

273
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:28,240
♪Flowers bloom and fall in shame♪

274
00:13:28,440 --> 00:13:34,960
♪If we meet again,
the peaches will be warm♪

275
00:13:35,320 --> 00:13:41,760
♪Spring breeze passes,
dancing through the years♪

276
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:48,440
♪Brewing longing,
remembering past lives♪

277
00:13:48,960 --> 00:13:55,640
♪Hard to meet, and just as hard to part♪

278
00:13:55,640 --> 00:14:02,520
♪Who planted the beans
that grew into lotuses?♪

279
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:08,640
♪Spring breeze passes,
composing the fleeting years♪

280
00:14:09,560 --> 00:14:16,160
♪Clouds on Mount Wu,
no sails on the sea♪

281
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:23,000
♪Wanting to fold my heart
into a paper kite♪

282
00:14:23,280 --> 00:14:29,720
♪But the ties are too tangled to sever♪

